events.name: クレア
events.note: プライオリティの調整のため、ページを複数に分けている

parameters: Adventurer Armada: Are you ready? I'm always prepared.
Clea: Don't worry. Let's definitely get some accessories.
Adventurer Armada: Of course! Now, come with me!

Explorer Armada: It's really cold at this altitude, so it's
a good thing we found a cave...
Clea: Is this the place around here?

Explorer Armada: If my prediction is correct, it seems like
the place they finally arrived at is Mount Monimos.

Explorer Armada: To think that we've cornered them this far,
even with their advanced civilization... The legend of the
hero might not be just a myth after all.

Priestess Sophia: Oh, what's wrong, Relm-chan? This wine
is...hic...the best for the cold, you know.

Mage Relm: Look! There's a statue of a dragon, just like the
one in that room.
Mage Relm: Armada-san... luck might be on our side!

Explorer Armada: Indeed, it's the same as what was in that
room... Phoni, can I ask you a favor?
Priestess Phoni: Yes, leave it to me!

Priestess Phoni: I will try the same as last time, touching
the statue... and channeling the voice of the dragon!

Explorer Armada: It seems like it went well! Now, show us...
the magic circle for us!

Explorer Armada: The final ruins to go beyond the room with
the door... When you're ready, let me know and we'll
proceed.
Clea: Haa... everyone is here. I'm really glad.

Thief Nora: Geez... It's all because of Armada-san and Relm-
san!

Explorer Armada: I'm really sorry for getting everyone
involved with my curiosity...
Mage Relm: Um... that... I'm sorry.

Priestess Sophia: Well, well, since everyone is safe, let's
have a drink and feel alive, huh~
Priestess Phoni: This sound... could it be...!?

Explorer Armada: I'm sorry, but... let me apologize again at
the foot of the mountain.
Bard: It's been a while since I came to Mount Monimos.
Bard: Well, if I don't fulfill my duty...

Bard: Oh, small sun of Sol... bestow upon this foolish
civilization a merciless judgment.
Clea (If you don't talk to Armada-san)
